    "description": "Gold-accented clean business consulting layout with advisory forms.",
    "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200",
    "featured": false,
    "html": "<div class=\"bg-[#FAF7F2] text-gray-900 font-serif min-h-screen flex flex-col\">\n  <!-- Header / Nav -->\n  <header class=\"w-full bg-[#FAF7F2] border-b border-[#0b1b3d]/10 px-8 py-5 flex items-center justify-between sticky top-0 z-50\">\n    <div class=\"font-bold text-lg uppercase text-[#0b1b3d] tracking-widest\">ConsultPro</div>\n    <nav class=\"hidden md:flex gap-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#0b1b3d]/60 font-sans\">\n      <a href=\"#brief\" class=\"text-[#0b1b3d]\">Advisory</a>\n      <a href=\"#services\" class=\"hover:text-[#0b1b3d] transition-colors\">Capabilities</a>\n      <a href=\"#team\" class=\"hover:text-[#0b1b3d] transition-colors\">Team</a>\n      <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"hover:text-[#0b1b3d] transition-colors\">Request Callback</a>\n    </nav>\n    <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"bg-[#0b1b3d] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded text-xs font-bold uppercase font-sans tracking-wider hover:bg-[#C19A5B] transition-colors\">Consultation</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- Hero Brief section -->\n  <main id=\"brief\" class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\">\n    <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n      <span class=\"text-[#C19A5B] text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest bg-[#C19A5B]/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full font-sans\">Corporate Advisory</span>\n      <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#0b1b3d]\">Strategic Consulting for Infrastructure Investment</h2>\n      <p class=\"text-[#0b1b3d]/70 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">ConsultPro Advisory offers procedural asset management, industrial mergers advisory, and risk assessment schemas for institutional partners.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"aspect-video rounded-xl bg-stone-200 overflow-hidden shadow-md\">\n      <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497215728101-856f4ea42174?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n    </div>\n  </main>\n\n  <!-- Services / Capabilities -->\n  <section id=\"services\" class=\"py-20 px-8 bg-white border-y border-[#0b1b3d]/10\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-12\">\n      <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-center text-[#0b1b3d]\">Core Advisory Capabilities</h3>\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-sm font-sans\">\n        <div class=\"p-6 bg-[#FAF7F2] rounded-xl border border-stone-200 space-y-2\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold text-[#0b1b3d] text-base\">Capital Allocation</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-stone-500 text-xs leading-relaxed\">Systematic diagnostics on corporate investments and asset diversification mappings.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-6 bg-[#FAF7F2] rounded-xl border border-stone-200 space-y-2\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold text-[#0b1b3d] text-base\">Risk Telemetry</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-stone-500 text-xs leading-relaxed\">Risk analysis dashboards mapping potential asset exposure variables.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"p-6 bg-[#FAF7F2] rounded-xl border border-stone-200 space-y-2\">\n          <h4 class=\"font-bold text-[#0b1b3d] text-base\">Operational Audits</h4>\n          <p class=\"text-stone-500 text-xs leading-relaxed\">Thorough procedural auditing for scaling corporate logistics workflows.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Team Section -->\n  <section id=\"team\" class=\"py-20 px-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-12\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-[#0b1b3d] text-center\">Senior Partners</h3>\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-center font-sans\">\n      <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n        <div class=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto overflow-hidden bg-stone-100 shadow-sm border border-stone-200\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522071820081-009f0129c71c?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=200\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm text-[#0b1b3d]\">Marcus Vance</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-xs text-[#C19A5B]\">Principal Partner &middot; Capital Infrastructure</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"space-y-3\">\n        <div class=\"w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto overflow-hidden bg-stone-100 shadow-sm border border-stone-200\">\n          <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534528741775-53994a69daeb?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=200\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n        </div>\n        <h4 class=\"font-bold text-sm text-[#0b1b3d]\">Sarah Jenkins</h4>\n        <p class=\"text-xs text-[#C19A5B]\">Principal Partner &middot; Industrial Mergers</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Request Consulting Brief -->\n  <section id=\"contact\" class=\"py-20 px-8 bg-white border-t border-[#0b1b3d]/10\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-md mx-auto space-y-6\">\n      <div class=\"text-center space-y-2\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900\">Request Consulting Brief</h3>\n        <p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 font-sans\">Submit details for a representative callback.</p>\n      </div>\n      <form data-studiopro-form data-form-name=\"ConsultPro Inquiry\" class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 font-sans\">\n        <div>\n          <label class=\"text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider\">Email Address</label>\n          <input name=\"email\" type=\"email\" class=\"w-full mt-1.5 p-3.5 bg-white border border-gray-300 rounded text-sm outline-none focus:border-[#C19A5B]\" placeholder=\"executive@firm.com\" required />\n        </div>\n        <button class=\"bg-[#0b1b3d] text-white py-3.5 rounded font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-xs hover:bg-[#C19A5B] transition-colors\" type=\"submit\">Submit Request</button>\n      </form>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <footer class=\"w-full bg-[#0b1b3d] text-gray-400 py-6 px-8 text-center text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mt-auto font-sans\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center\">\n      <span>CONSULT PRO ADVISORY &copy; 2026</span>\n      <span>London &middot; New York</span>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>",
