    "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620916566398-39f1143ab7be?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200",
    "featured": false,
    "html": "<div class=\"bg-[#FAF7F2] text-[#2B2724] font-sans min-h-screen flex flex-col\">\n  <!-- Navbar -->\n  <header class=\"w-full border-b border-[#2B2724]/10 bg-[#FAF7F2] px-8 py-5 flex items-center justify-between sticky top-0 z-50\">\n    <div class=\"font-serif text-lg tracking-widest text-[#2B2724] uppercase\">AURA.</div>\n    <nav class=\"hidden md:flex gap-8 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#766A60]\">\n      <a href=\"#products\" class=\"text-[#2B2724]\">Botanicals</a>\n      <a href=\"#focus\" class=\"hover:text-[#2B2724] transition-colors\">Ingredients</a>\n      <a href=\"#newsletter\" class=\"hover:text-[#2B2724] transition-colors\">Newsletter</a>\n    </nav>\n    <button data-action=\"open-cart\" class=\"bg-[#2B2724] text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-full font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-[#4A443E] transition-colors active:scale-95\">\n      Bag\n    </button>\n  </header>\n\n  <!-- Hero Banner -->\n  <section class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8 py-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center\">\n    <div class=\"space-y-6\">\n      <span class=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#766A60]\">ESSENTIAL SKINCARE</span>\n      <h1 class=\"text-5xl font-serif text-[#2B2724] leading-tight font-light\">Organic botanical layouts for deep cellular hydration.</h1>\n      <p class=\"text-sm text-[#766A60] leading-relaxed\">Formulated with cold-pressed rosehip seed oil, telemetry botanical extracts, and natural essential plant enzymes for cellular recovery.</p>\n      <a href=\"#products\" class=\"inline-block bg-[#2B2724] text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-[#4A443E] transition-colors\">Browse Botanicals</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"aspect-[4/5] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden bg-[#EAE3D9] shadow-sm\">\n      <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620916566398-39f1143ab7be?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Products Grid -->\n  <section id=\"products\" class=\"py-20 bg-[#EAE3D9]/30 border-y border-[#2B2724]/10 px-8\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto space-y-12\">\n      <div class=\"text-center space-y-2\">\n        <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-serif font-light text-[#2B2724]\">Our Botanicals</h2>\n        <p class=\"text-xs text-[#766A60] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">Organic skincare formulas</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n        <article class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[#2B2724]/5 space-y-4 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div class=\"aspect-square w-full rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-[#FAF7F2]\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1620916566398-39f1143ab7be?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"space-y-1\">\n            <h3 class=\"font-serif text-[#2B2724] text-lg\">Aura Hydrating Mist</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-[#766A60]\">$28.00</p>\n          </div>\n          <button data-action=\"open-cart\" class=\"w-full py-2 bg-[#2B2724] hover:bg-[#4A443E] text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold rounded-full transition-colors active:scale-95\">Add to Bag</button>\n        </article>\n        <article class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 border border-[#2B2724]/5 space-y-4 flex flex-col justify-between\">\n          <div class=\"aspect-square w-full rounded-t-xl overflow-hidden bg-[#FAF7F2]\">\n            <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505740420928-5e560c06d30e?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"space-y-1\">\n            <h3 class=\"font-serif text-[#2B2724] text-lg\">Essential Cleansing Oil</h3>\n            <p class=\"text-xs text-[#766A60]\">$24.00</p>\n          </div>\n          <button data-action=\"open-cart\" class=\"w-full py-2 bg-[#2B2724] hover:bg-[#4A443E] text-white text-xs uppercase tracking-wider font-bold rounded-full transition-colors active:scale-95\">Add to Bag</button>\n        </article>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Ingredients focus spotlight -->\n  <section id=\"focus\" class=\"py-20 px-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-12\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-serif text-center font-light\">Organic Ingredients Integrity</h3>\n    <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center text-xs font-bold font-sans uppercase\">\n      <div class=\"p-6 bg-white border border-[#2B2724]/10 rounded-2xl\">Rosehip Seed Oil</div>\n      <div class=\"p-6 bg-white border border-[#2B2724]/10 rounded-2xl\">Aloe Leaf Extract</div>\n      <div class=\"p-6 bg-white border border-[#2B2724]/10 rounded-2xl\">Sweet Almond Telemetry</div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Newsletter -->\n  <section id=\"newsletter\" class=\"py-20 px-8 text-center max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-6\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-serif font-light text-[#2B2724]\">JOIN THE DISPATCH</h3>\n    <p class=\"text-xs text-[#766A60]\">Subscribe for beauty research blogs, product catalog releases, and 15% off coupon codes.</p>\n    <form data-studiopro-form data-form-name=\"Aura Subscriber\" class=\"flex gap-2\">\n      <input name=\"email\" type=\"email\" class=\"flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-[#EAE3D9]/30 border border-[#2B2724]/20 text-[#2B2724] rounded-full text-xs outline-none focus:border-[#2B2724]\" placeholder=\"email@address.com\" required />\n      <button class=\"bg-[#2B2724] hover:bg-[#4A443E] text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full transition-colors\" type=\"submit\">Join</button>\n    </form>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <footer class=\"w-full bg-[#2B2724] text-[#FAF7F2]/50 py-8 px-12 text-center text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mt-auto\">\n    <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center\">\n      <span>AURA BOTANICALS &copy; 2026</span>\n      <span>Organic Skincare</span>\n    </div>\n  </footer>\n</div>",
    "css": ""
